[Any hunter who is able should have the game sampled for chronic wasting disease. This is a type of surveillance that allows authorities to know if the disease is spreading to other areas, as in this case. - Mod.TG

The state of Michigan can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5375154,225. A county map can be seen at http://geology.com/county-map/michigan-county-map.gif. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
